# Voice models are large (~350 MB total) and exceed GitHub's 100 MB
# per-file limit. They are downloaded at Docker-build time instead of
# being committed to the repo (see Dockerfile, deferred to follow-up
# batch). For local dev, run scripts/download-voices.sh to fetch them.
*.onnx
*.onnx.json

# Keep the README so the directory exists in git
!.gitignore
!README.md
